DataElement.preferredName: Material Storage Administration Performed Study Activity Status Date and Time ISO21090.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed action of safekeeping harvested material in a depository. EXAMPLE(S): refrigeration, cryopreservation, dehydration, etc. NOTE(S): There is a difference between the act of changing the state of material, and the act of maintaining state of the material by storing it, which is represented here. The date (and time) on which the status is assigned to the activity.
